room_title: Escape room "The Secret of Scully's Cabin" by Escape LOU in Louisville
room_description: A chain of vanishing hikers in the area has local law enforcement perplexed. You and your team of FBI agents have been called in to lead the mysterious investigation. As you search deep into the stormy, sinister woods,  you encounter an abandoned cabin that is absent from the map. What has become of the missing hikers? And what secrets will you uncover during your 60 minutes inside the deserted dwelling?
